instanceVariables.name: JumpDelay
instanceVariables.desc: Delay between two jump of the object implementing Jumper.

instanceVariables.name: JumpDefaultStrength
instanceVariables.desc: Default strength of the jump of the object implementing Jumper.

instanceVariables.name: JumpCurrentBoost
instanceVariables.desc: Current bonus to apply on the Vector Y component of the jump of the object implementing Jumper.

instanceVariables.name: JumpDefaultMaxCount
instanceVariables.desc: Default number of jumps which can be performed by the object implementing Jumper before it reaches the ground.

instanceVariables.name: JumpRemaining
instanceVariables.desc: Current number of jumps remaining which can be performed by the object implementing Jumper before it reaches the ground, whence it will be reset to the JumpDefaultMaxCount.
